OL,7,FThe mother of a teenager who took his
OL,8,Fown life after spending time in an
OL,9,Fadult psychiatric ward has branded the
OL,10,Fjudge-led inquiry into his death a
OL,11,F"missed opportunity."
OL,13,FHarris Macdonell died on August 19th
OL,14,F2020, at the age of 19, near his home
OL,15,Fin Lilliesleaf in the Scottish Borders.
OL,17,FHis family campaigned for the Fatal
OL,18,FAccident Inquiry which took place
OL,19,Fearlier this year.
