OL,7,FLast week, it concluded that his death
OL,8,Fcould not have been prevented.
OL,10,FIn a letter to Sheriff Paterson, who
OL,11,Fled the inquiry, Jane Macdonnell
OL,12,Fwrote: "This was an opportunity to
OL,13,Freally challenge the NHS and prevent
OL,14,Ffuture deaths. It has been missed."
OL,16,FIn 2018, aged 16, Harris spent nine
OL,17,Fnights in Huntlyburn, NHS Borders'
OL,18,Fadult psychiatric ward near Melrose,
OL,19,Fbefore a bed became available in a
OL,20,Fyoung persons unit in Edinburgh.
