OL,7,FDuring that time, he ran away from the
OL,8,Fward and was picked up by staff on the
OL,9,Fside of the road. He jumped from the
OL,10,Fcar while it was driving, sustaining
OL,11,Fserious injuries, in an attempt to
OL,12,Fescape.
OL,14,FThe Sheriff's determination
OL,15,Frecommended that the entrance and exit
OL,16,Fto Huntlyburn should be controlled.
OL,18,FThe report also said that it was
OL,19,F"wholly inappropriate" for young
OL,20,Fpeople to be treated in adult wards.
