OL,7,FJane said: "I was quite clear that I
OL,8,Fagreed with him about locked doors and
OL,9,Fthat there is a lack of adolescent
OL,10,Fappropriate beds, but I think that's a
OL,11,Fvery easy conclusion to draw from
OL,12,Fthis. I'm not sure why he hasn't gone
OL,13,Finto more depth in his determination
OL,14,Fbut he has certainly not tackled the
OL,15,Fdifficult aspects of it."
