OL,4,Clife brands inquiry a 'missed
OL,5,Copportunity'
OL,7,F"The absolute bottom line is that you
OL,8,Fhave a young person in an adult ward,
OL,9,Fwho's becoming distressed, that needs
OL,10,Fto be an emergency. That's not
OL,11,Facceptable."
OL,13,FDr Lynn Mccallum, medical director at
OL,14,FNHS Borders, said: "We respect the
OL,15,FSheriff's determination, that in
OL,16,Fconsidering the evidence submitted,
OL,17,FHarris's death could not have been
OL,18,Fpredicted or prevented.
