OL,7,F"In relation to Sheriff Paterson's
OL,8,Frecommendations about controlled
OL,9,Faccess to Huntlyburn Ward, NHS Borders
OL,10,Ffollows Mental Welfare Commission
OL,11,Fguidelines and an entry / exit system
OL,12,Fis in place. We will reach out to the
OL,13,FCommission to seek their views on the
OL,14,Frecommendation made."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Judicial Office
OL,17,Ffor Scotland said: "We extend our
OL,18,Fcondolences to the family of Harris
OL,19,FMacdonell for their loss.
