OL,7,F"The purpose of a Fatal Accident
OL,8,FInquiry is to establish the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of a death and consider
OL,10,Fwhat steps (if any) might
OL,11,Frealistically be taken to prevent
OL,12,Fother deaths in similar circumstances.
OL,14,F"In any inquiry, sheriffs carefully
OL,15,Fconsider all of the evidence presented
OL,16,Fbefore reaching their determination
OL,17,Fand making any appropriate
OL,18,Frecommendations."
