OL,7,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We expect children and young
OL,9,Fpeople who need inpatient mental
OL,10,Fhealth care to be looked after in age-
OL,11,Fappropriate specialist facilities.
OL,13,F"On occasions where young people are
OL,14,Fplaced within an adult ward this will
OL,15,Fbe monitored and reviewed regularly to
OL,16,Fensure that the young person is
OL,17,Freceiving the most appropriate
OL,18,Ftreatment and care."
